MTN will launch a promotion on 8 August 2018 which will reward customers for downloading the MyMTN app. All first-time users who download the app from this date will receive a free 1GB data bundle. The MyMTN app can be used to purchase airtime and data bundles, monitor data usage, and pay bills. The 1GB free data promotion will then run until 31 December 2018 â€“ with the data valid for one day, activated within 24 hours of the app download. Customers will be notified when their 1GB free data bundle has been activated. The MyMTN app is free to download from the Google Play or Apple App stores.